Current Provider API Endpoint

Source: R/S7_backend.R
Provider.Rd

Current Provider API Endpoint

Usage

proMain(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <proMain> object.

Examples

proMain("affiliations")
#> ── Facility Affiliation Data ──
#> 
#>   This is the facility affiliations data
#>   publicly reported in the Provider Data
#>   Catalog.
#> 
#> • Rows 1,566,867
#> • Pages 784
#> • Fields 9
#> 
#> • Issued ❯ 2023-08-17
#> • Modified ❯ 2025-03-24
#> • Released ❯ 2025-04-03
proMain("clinicians")
#> ── National Downloadable File ──
#> 
#>   The Doctors and Clinicians national
#>   downloadable file is organized such that
#>   each line is unique at the
#>   clinician/enrollment record/group/address
#>   level. Clinicians with multiple Medicare
#>   enrollment records and/or single
#>   enrollments linking to multiple practice
#>   locations are listed on multiple lines.
#> 
#> • Rows 2,631,270
#> • Pages 1,316
#> • Fields 31
#> 
#> • Issued ❯ 2023-08-17
#> • Modified ❯ 2025-03-24
#> • Released ❯ 2025-04-03
proMain("utilization")
#> ── Utilization Data ──
#> 
#>   The Doctors and Clinicians utilization
#>   data file reports volume information for
#>   procedures of interest on clinician
#>   profile pages and in the provider data
#>   catalog (PDC) to inform patients and
#>   caregivers about clinicians' experience.
#> 
#> • Rows 301,894
#> • Pages 151
#> • Fields 10
#> 
#> • Issued ❯ 2024-01-04
#> • Modified ❯ 2025-03-24
#> • Released ❯ 2025-04-03
